497
00:57:37,082 --> 00:57:49,782
♬｢The fundamental things apply
As time goes by｣

498
00:57:53,131 --> 00:57:56,801
♬｢And when two lovers woo｣

499
00:57:56,801 --> 00:58:00,672
♬｢They still say
